current_status_notes: Applied online via link on megathread, went to pending 7-10 days. Called auto status line said 2 weeks. Called recon, needed to verify personal info and income, then said they could submit it for a final sign-off to get more credit (because i was at max exposure) or they could approve now if I shifted some CL's. Went with shifting CL's for instant approval. Initially said needed 10k to open account, then said 14k. Shifted 5k CSP, 4K CF, 5K Chase PP to get 14K. Called regular customer service line to get expedited shipping, change of shipping address and CONFIRMED that 100k bonus was on my account (CS rep said some links arent showing it but it will show up on all links within 48hrs, FWIW). Fantastic day after some negotiation!
